there is three type of errors : 
1 : syntax error  ==> when you forget a semicolon or a bracket ....

2 : logical error ==> when the programe work but the resulte in the output are wrong

3 : run time error ==> when the programe blocked for some reason

What is debugging ?
debugging is the ability to run the code line by line to trease the variables and 
values and functions that you have in the programe
